Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!來吧!雪之丞!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,片名:明日的雪之丞2 MASARU
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二章 藍色的復活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關掉車燈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:03:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才經過的路 有條林道可以進入別墅區
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必要時可以用這女人為人質
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真紀小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了 這是妳的別墅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正確的說法是爸爸他們的別墅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他太忙了 現在就變成我專用的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管那個 我們來盡情享受屬於我倆的假日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳太美麗了 真紀小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接喊我的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒 要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真紀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝 我們一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦才好呢?我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分手?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來我只是大小姐消磨時間的玩伴之一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你若希望那樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就那樣想吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 來吧 雪之丞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不像平時的阿勝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久保
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪之丞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探病
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:09:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像很健康
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一是來探病 二是回程的巴士沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些藉口真完美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別胡說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我說中了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要回去了哦 虧我們是這麼擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑的 我很歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真紀 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像很好的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳在別墅嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:11:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想春天已經到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼好冷 我就生爐火了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!你等一下!火快滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的朋友在這裡等耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿她沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你遲遲沒下來 我們就自己進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電話中啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉 馬上就談完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了?真紀?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了?真紀!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 放開我 回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…不要那麼粗魯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小明的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小明是…?水島嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病人房間怎麼會有這個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好安靜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有聽說他們是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到是那種關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!大哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人在 好像只有那個女人的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我發現好東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是大功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四周的別墅都沒人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我們與兩位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快樂派對的要素都聚集了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像弄壞什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳擔心妳自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:14:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟警察講是真紀的別墅 警方就會知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上連絡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫吧 叫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四周沒有半個人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點也沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣我們的派對才玩得起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我 阿勝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.01,0:19:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪之丞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擂台上再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直到之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己都沒發現自己這麼喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我察覺時 自己的眼神已經只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小明 我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你溫柔一點 拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太美麗了 小明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣盯著人家 好難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.46,0:21:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 不好意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.48,0:21:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝 這次換我來為你口交吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.84,0:21:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小明 太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.67,0:22:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.55,0:22:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝 好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你 要溫柔 不能粗魯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.21,0:23:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好有感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.42,0:23:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我與阿勝現在合而為一了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.17,0:24:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒 好舒服啊 阿勝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.04,0:24:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後我們也會一直在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.12,0:24:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝 我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡你!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.67,0:24:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.61,0:24:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要高潮了 我…要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.74,0:24:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.88,0:24:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.69,0:24:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.23,0:25:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再插了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.37,0:25:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為妳 我又恢復元氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.91,0:25:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.98,0:25:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會有感覺 有感覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.63,0:26:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我來了 雪之丞
